<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.11">
<l>marutap poḻilaṇi māliruñ cōlai malaitaṉṉai</l>
<l>karuti yuṟaikiṉṟa kārkkaṭal vaṇṇaṉam māṉtaṉṉai</l>
<l>virataṅ koṇṭēttum villiput tūrviṭṭu cittaṉcol</l>
<l>karuti yuraippavar kaṇṇaṉ kaḻaliṇaikāṇ pārkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who meditatively recite the words of Viṭṭucittaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">[who dwells in] Villiputtūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">where, having taken a vow, he praised</l>
<l>the lord of dark ocean hue, who dwells intentionally</l>
<l rend="indent">[on] the mountain of Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">adorned with maruta groves,</l>
<l>they will see Kaṇṇaṉ’s pair of anklets.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
